  "instructions": [
    "Rub a lemon wedge along the upper half inch of a collins glass, halfway around the circumference, then roll the wet portion in kosher salt.",
    "Pour beer into the glass. Shake remaining ingredients with ice, then strain into the glass. Fill with ice cubes. No garnish."
